page.title: 20BIRDS
page.content: These are the wild birds we saw during our nature survey of the N.W.part of Havering.We did not have anyone with us who really knew about birds so we had to rely on our bird "spotter"books and the binoculars we had borrowed from the borough's science centre. {pheasant white throat {skylark pied wagtail {wren thrush {bullfinch coal tit {magpies sparrow {crow blackbird {cuckoo starling {robin blue tit {goldfinch yellow hammer {mallard ducks greenfinch {owl swift {jay collared dove {wood pigeon feral pigeon {warbler moorhen
